My Friday:

1. Packing for myself, River and Bella to leave for Vancouver tomorrow for our show on Sunday. 
2. Composing my discussion board post for next week. 
3. Doing research for my critique paper also due next week. 

Ohhh boy..Lord help me 🙏🏻😩

#fnpstudent #mamalife

Been stranded at the Denver airport since last night..trying to get to Vancouver for a show tonight..flights are still getting cancelled one after the other. Hundreds of people stranded. 

😔😔😔 

My babies have really good this whole time. I’m a lucky momma ♥️ 

What happened @united ???

Still stuck in Denver. Will try to flyout to Vancouver this morning. Flight arrives to Vancouver around 430pm..show is at 7pm…

Hopefully we get on…🙁🙏🏻

#zombiemode #stranded #unitedairlines #canceledflight

Arrived in Vancouver around 4pm. Got to the baggage claim only to find out that NONE of our 4 checked baggage made it. 

😩😩😩

I was trying my best to keep myself calm. My son said, “Mama, don’t worry, we will make it to your show. And don’t worry about how you will look, just sing…” ♥️ Went to the venue with nothing but just the clothes we had on for 2 days.

Shoutout to Ate @imacastro1 for graciously lending me one of her gowns and also her shoes ♥️ buti na lang we have the same shoe size 😂 Also want to thank @dessapowerhousediva for taking care of my other needs (make up, perfume) since I had nothing with me. ♥️ Love you both 😘

Also want to thank Ate Goldie of #REtroSPECT for lending me her clothes for our Finale number ♥️ 

You ladies rock and I appreciate what you have done for me so much ♥️ 

It’s a wrap for me for this tour. Thank you so much @jaroproductionsusa! 

@sherynregis congratulations again on your 20th year in the business! Keep on shining and singing with that beautiful and powerful voice that you have ♥️
